  "name": "Business Proposal / Price Quote",
  "description": "A formal document outlining the scope of work, timeline, and pricing for products or services offered to a client.",
  "price": 10,
  "language": "en",
  "slug": "business-proposal-price-quote",
  "content": "<div style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee;'>\n<h2 style='text-align:center; margin-bottom: 25px;'>PROPOSAL / QUOTATION</h2>\n\n<div style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 25px; flex-wrap: wrap;'>\n <div style='flex-basis: 48%;'>\n <p><strong>Submitted By:</strong></p>\n <p>{{provider_name_company}}<br/>\n {{provider_address}}<br/>\n {{#if provider_tax_id}}Tax ID / VAT: {{provider_tax_id}}<br/>{{/if}}\n Tel: {{provider_phone}}<br/>\n Email: {{provider_email}}\n </p>\n </div>\n <div style='flex-basis: 48%; text-align: right;'>\n <p><strong>Quote No:</strong> {{quote_number}}</p>\n <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{formatDate quote_date}}</p>\n <p><strong>Valid Until:</strong> {{validity_days}} Days from Date</p>\n </div>\n</div>\n\n<hr style='margin: 20px 0;'/>\n\n<p><strong>Submitted To (Client):</strong></p>\n<p>{{client_name_company}}<br/>\n{{client_address}}<br/>\n{{#if client_contact_person}}Attn: {{client_contact_person}}<br/>{{/if}}\n{{#if client_phone}}Tel: {{client_phone}}<br/>{{/if}}\n{{#if client_email}}Email: {{client_email}}{{/if}}\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Project/Subject:</strong> {{quote_subject}}</p>\n\n<p>Dear {{#if client_contact_person}}{{client_contact_person}}{{else}}{{client_name_company}}{{/if}},</p>\n<p>Thank you for the opportunity to provide this proposal. Based on our discussions, please find our scope of work and pricing below regarding {{quote_subject}}:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Scope of Work / Deliverables:</strong></p>\n<pre style='white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word;'>{{scope_of_work}}</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Pricing & Breakdown:</strong></p>\n<pre style='white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word;'>{{pricing_details}}</pre>\n<p><strong>Grand Total: {{grand_total}} (Excluding Applicable Taxes)</strong></p>\n\n{{#if estimated_timeline}}\n<p><strong>Estimated Timeline:</strong> {{estimated_timeline}}</p>\n{{/if}}\n\n<p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong></p>\n<pre style='white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word;'>{{payment_terms}}</pre>\n\n{{#if additional_notes}}\n<p><strong>Additional Notes / Terms:</strong></p>\n<pre style='white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word;'>{{additional_notes}}</pre>\n{{/if}}\n\n<p>If you have any questions or require modifications to this proposal, please do not hesitate to contact us. To accept this quote, please sign below and return a copy to us.</p>\n\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\n\n<div style='margin-top: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;'>\n <div style='flex-basis: 48%;'>\n <p><strong>Provider Signature</strong><br/><br/>\n <span style='display: inline-block; margin-top: 15px;'>_________________________</span><br/>\n {{provider_name_company}}\n </p>\n </div>\n <div style='flex-basis: 48%;'>\n <p><strong>Client Acceptance</strong><br/><br/>\n <span style='display: inline-block; margin-top: 15px;'>_________________________</span><br/>\n Date: _____________\n </p>\n </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
